job.title: SSC Constable GD Recruitment 2021  Apply Online for 25271 Various Vacancies in India
job.body:
Total vacancies:25271

Name of the Vacancies:

  • Constable GD

Description

Latest Central Government Jobs for the 10th pass has been published by Staff Selection Commission for Constable GD vacancies in India. If you are searching for a government job in India then it is an opportunity for you. You can fill the online application for the vacancies of Constable GD, from 17-07-2021, and till 31-08-2021 (23:30). If you are interested in all these vacancies in India and if eligible, please check out the details given below, which have been given age limit, educational qualification pay scale, etc.

Application fee:

  • The mode of application is Online
  • The application fee for GEN/ OBC category candidates is only Rs. 100/-

Educational qualification:

  • To apply for a Constable GD  in SSC, your 10th class must be completed from a recognized University

Important dates:

  •  The starting date to apply in these posts is 17-07-2021
  •  The last date to apply in these posts is 31-08-2021 (23:30)

Age Limit Criteria:

  • For General Candidate, you should be between 18 to 28 years old. 

SSC Constable GD Pay Scale:

  • According to the information given by the Central Government and as per the 7th pay commission, the teacher's monthly salary is as per norms

How to apply for SSC Constable GD Recruitment 2021?

Press the Apply Now button above. You can directly and easily start the application process of the Constable GD. Fill in your details and submit it or follow all the steps given below.

  •  First, go to the official website of SSC and register yourself on the portal.
  • Find the notification, log in and then provide the details and documents asked by SSC
  • Then save it and complete the application submission.
  • Then to fully complete the process you have to submit the application fee.
  • And finally, download the application form for future purposes.
